|WKBNAME|000
    set_shield

|WKBSYNOPSIS|000
    |YK0void|000 |CKBset_shield|000(|YK0int|000 |GKBiAmount|000)
    |YK0void|000 |CKBset_shield|000(|YK0int|000 |GKBiAmount|000, |YK0int|000 |GKBiType|000)

|WKBDESCRIPTION|000
    Set a living creature/player's shield for damage

    |GKBiAmount|000 is the amount of damage the shield will
    absorb or block [Required]

    |GKBiType|000 is an optional parameter (|YK0damage type|000) specifying the type of
    damage the shield will block/absorb.  If not specified, this is
    set the generic shield. May be useful to check <types.h>


    |CKBset_shield|000() is defined in /secure/living.c

|WKBSEE ALSO|000
    |CKBadd_shield|000(L), |CKBquery_shield|000(L), |CKBremove_shield|000(L)

